<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thagau, Thieng Puipa ginum,
 Kristien kawmah nai zingin
 Na khut in ei pui zelin,
 Gamgaw a khuolzin ka hiu;
 Tha chaute kipak zing ding,
 Aw ngaihnawp um pen chuh za'n;
 A gukcha'n &quot;Vakvai hungin!
 Ei zuiin, hun pui ingka.&quot;

[V2]
 2. Tikchan a um Guol ginum,
 Ei panpih zing zingin Aw;
 Thim lakah ginglah, lau di'n,
 Kei uh ei nusie ki'n la;
 Guohpi, huihpi hunghat tieng
 Lungdawng in, kinepna bei;
 Agukcha'n &quot;Vakvai, hungin,
 Ei zuiin hun pui ingka.&quot;

[V3]
 3. I sepgim niu abeih tieng,
 Chawlhna ding I ngak nalai;
 Van leh ngetna mai eitai,
 Ziechun I min um gingcha'n;
 Lungkham tui kinawk palin,
 Isu thisan mai ngenin,
 Agukcha'n &quot;Vakvai, hungin,
 Ei zuiin, hunpui ingka.&quot;</lyrics>
<title>HOLY SPIRIT, FAITHFUL GUIDE!</title>
</song>